    "body": "This PR add [`humming-kernels`](https://pypi.org/project/humming-kernels/) to dependencies.\r\n\r\nHumming does not have heavy dependencies. The following is the dependency list for `humming-kernels`:\r\n\r\n```\r\ndependencies = [\r\n    \"torch>=2.7\",\r\n    \"triton\",\r\n    \"numpy\",\r\n    \"safetensors\",\r\n    \"jinja2\",\r\n    \"pyelftools\",\r\n    \"nvidia-ml-py\",\r\n    \"cuda-bindings\",\r\n]\r\n\r\n[project.optional-dependencies]\r\ncu12 = [\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-runtime-cu12\",\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-cccl-cu12\",\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-nvcc-cu12\",\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-nvrtc-cu12\",\r\n]\r\ncu13 = [\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-runtime\",\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-cccl\",\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-nvcc\",\r\n    \"nvidia-cuda-nvrtc\",\r\n]\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2026-05-13T16:02:52Z",
